<section>
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>The <code>&lt;table-wc&gt;</code> component wraps a standard HTML table to provide interactive features like column sorting, text filtering, pagination, expandable rows, row selection with bulk actions, responsive card layouts, and sticky headers/columns. All features are opt-in via data attributes and the table remains fully functional without JavaScript.</p>

